    },
    {
      "air_date": "2010-09-26T00:00:00-07:00",
      "episode_count": 7,
      "id": 44728,
      "name": "Series 1",
      "overview": "Lord Robert Crawley and his family live a life of leisure, while a fleet of servants, including butler Carson, attend to their every need. But two events conspire to shake things up: the sinking of the Titanic, which claims Crawley\u0027s heirs, and the return of his valet, Bates. Since Crawley and Lady Cora have three daughters, his distant solicitor cousin, Matthew, becomes heir to the estate. With that, the scheming begins, since Thomas the footman views Bates as an interloper and Crawley\u0027s mother, Violet, feels the same way about Matthew\u0027s mother, Isobel.",
      "poster_path": "/wLOQuC8L552c4tJANu1UAI0CYf2.jpg",
      "season_number": 1
    },
    {
      "air_date": "2011-09-18T00:00:00-07:00",
      "episode_count": 8,
      "id": 44729,
      "name": "Series 2",
      "overview": "The Great War rages across Europe, and not even the serene Yorkshire countryside is free from its effects. The men and women of Downton are doing their part both on the front lines and the home front, but the intensity of war only serves to inflame the more familiar passions: love, loss, blackmail, and betrayal.",
      "poster_path": "/ilCoT7k9I5YjQntUqDHQqowNg30.jpg",
      "season_number": 2
    },
    {
      "air_date": "2012-09-16T00:00:00-07:00",
      "episode_count": 8,
      "id": 44730,
      "name": "Series 3",
      "overview": "The Great War is over and a long-awaited engagement is on, but all is not tranquil at Downton Abbey as wrenching social changes, romantic intrigues, and personal crises grip the majestic English country estate. As other great houses are crippled psychologically and financially in the wake of World War I, Robert, Earl of Grantham, sticks to his duty to maintain Downton more firmly than ever. But in this changing landscape nothing is assured, and could it be that even the war-weary Crawleys must fight a new battle to safeguard their beloved Downton?\u00A0",
      "poster_path": "/mNywtZcFOIN4Wv02KGA51GmLxog.jpg",
      "season_number": 3
    },
    {
      "air_date": "2013-09-15T00:00:00-07:00",
      "episode_count": 8,
      "id": 44731,
      "name": "Series 4",
      "overview": "Set in 1922, the fourth series sees\u00A0Lady Mary mourning her loss as\u00A0the Crawley family and the servants who work for them remain inseparably interlinked.",
      "poster_path": "/xWgcXulnKGiyCUV7m2Fa4Scv15f.jpg",
      "season_number": 4
    },
    {
      "air_date": "2014-09-21T00:00:00-07:00",
      "episode_count": 8,
      "id": 62638,
      "name": "Series 5",
      "overview": "Season 5 finds the Crawley family and the staff struggling with responsibilities and choices as they adjust to life in the Roaring Twenties.\u00A0A new Labour government heralds changes that are being felt throughout the land, and Robert, Mary and Branson together must navigate these shifting sands to ensure the future of the estate for generations to come. As Branson finds himself playing a more crucial role at Downton than ever before, he can\u2019t help questioning his place in this world. Mary is finally coming to accept that she would like to marry again, but will she ever be able to find the same happiness that she had with Matthew? Meanwhile with still no news of her beloved Gregson, Edith suffers under the burden of her terrible secret.",
      "poster_path": "/vfhiGuKW35QVl6zEfy8mxMZokHO.jpg",
      "season_number": 5
    },
    {
      "air_date": "2015-09-20T00:00:00-07:00",
      "episode_count": 8,
      "id": 69183,
      "name": "Series 6",
      "overview": "Our time with the Crawleys draws to a close and we see what will finally become of them all.\u00A0Secrets and rifts threaten the unity of the family, while those below stairs continue to navigate social changes which put their futures in jeopardy. Will Mary choose the right path? Will her sister Edith finally get a break?! Will Carson and Mrs Hughes actually make it up the aisle? And will Anna and Bates overcome the many hurdles that have been set before them?",
      "poster_path": "/af3bZuN5wCRn5JEi1jIZ3cPZ1Sp.jpg",
      "season_number": 6
    }
  ],
